OL,3,CUK unemployment jumps to highest since
OL,4,C2021 as wage growth slows
OL,6,FBritain's jobless rate has risen to
OL,7,F4.7%, its highest level for four
OL,8,Fyears, as workers also faced another
OL,9,Fslowdown in wage growth, official
OL,10,Ffigures have shown.
OL,12,FAccording to the Office for National
OL,13,FStatistics (ONS), the rate of UK
OL,14,Funemployment increased by 0.1% in the
OL,15,Fthree months to May from 4.6% in the
OL,16,Fthree months to April.
OL,18,FMeanwhile, average earnings growth,
OL,19,Fexcluding bonuses, slowed to 5% in the
OL,20,Fperiod to May to its lowest level for
OL,21,Falmost three years.
