OL,3,CUK unemployment jumps to highest since
OL,4,C2021 as wage growth slows
OL,6,FThe figures point towards further
OL,7,Fpressure in the UK labour market, days
OL,8,Fafter the governor of the Bank of
OL,9,FEngland warned that the Bank is
OL,10,Fprepared to make larger interest rate
OL,11,Fcuts if it sees that the job market is
OL,12,Fslowing.
OL,14,FONS director of economic statistics
OL,15,FLiz McKeown said: "The labour market
OL,16,Fcontinues to weaken, with the number
OL,17,Fof employees on payroll falling again,
OL,18,Fthough revised tax data shows the
OL,19,Fdecline in recent months is less
OL,20,Fpronounced than previously estimated.
